 narrative when making videos for businesses, even if they don't seem as flashy as movies or fictional series. I hope this has helped you understand the different shots and angles. Don't forget to subscribe so you don't miss any more! Videos like this are great, and if you have any questions, feel free to leave them in the comments. Also, if there's a cool shot you think we missed, let us know in the comments too. See you next week with a new video here on Dominical. Bye!

